This will become an issue for me as I am waiting for 2.4 to solve &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MJAVADOC-135&quot; title=&quot;Error parsing javadoc version when used with IBM jdk 1.4.2&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MJAVADOC-135&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MJAVADOC-135&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
